1
00:00:35,959 --> 00:00:38,854
♪Traversing the vast expanse of time♪

2
00:00:38,872 --> 00:00:42,399
♪Smiling proudly
in the mortal world alone♪

3
00:00:42,944 --> 00:00:45,130
♪Cold moonlight♪

4
00:00:45,440 --> 00:00:48,928
♪Earth as paper, sky as brush♪

5
00:00:48,928 --> 00:00:53,439
♪This life like ink splashed on paper♪

6
00:00:53,439 --> 00:00:56,233
♪Indulging in ups and downs♪

7
00:00:56,233 --> 00:00:58,688
♪Coldly confronting
the approaching edges, sword and blade♪

8
00:00:58,688 --> 00:01:01,120
♪My heart is narrow,
only holding heaven and earth♪

9
00:01:01,120 --> 00:01:06,528
♪Boundless sea,
countless surging waves in the dark♪

10
00:01:06,528 --> 00:01:09,041
♪Aeons just like a fleeting moment,
using youth as color♪

11
00:01:09,041 --> 00:01:11,392
♪A silver-white hue climbs up
the temples, undaunted by setbacks♪

12
00:01:11,392 --> 00:01:16,177
♪In the eyes, an unquenchable light♪

13
00:01:16,179 --> 00:01:18,791
♪A body of proud bones,
unbending in the face of wind and frost♪

14
00:01:18,791 --> 00:01:21,216
♪Smiling at the thorny webs♪

15
00:01:21,216 --> 00:01:26,697
♪Being a lone wolf,
born to be solitary and independent♪

16
00:01:26,697 --> 00:01:29,024
♪My pride alters not a jot♪

17
00:01:29,024 --> 00:01:31,392
♪Resounding loudly through the clouds♪

18
00:01:31,392 --> 00:01:38,912
♪In the cold world,
a heart burning hot for you♪

19
00:01:38,912 --> 00:01:42,950
=Snow Eagle Lord=

20
00:01:43,403 --> 00:01:45,708
=Episode 24=

21
00:01:56,990 --> 00:01:57,550
Master.

22
00:02:00,071 --> 00:02:01,311
Xueying.

23
00:02:01,630 --> 00:02:02,990
Master, are you there?

24
00:02:11,910 --> 00:02:12,591
Master,

25
00:02:13,711 --> 00:02:15,151
why did you hurt so bad?

26
00:02:15,510 --> 00:02:16,591
I'm fine.

27
00:02:17,070 --> 00:02:17,950
Have a seat.

28
00:02:18,591 --> 00:02:19,991
Take your time.

29
00:02:21,311 --> 00:02:22,151
Xueying.

30
00:02:22,711 --> 00:02:23,551
Fighting against the Demon Clan

31
00:02:23,551 --> 00:02:24,991
is not an easy task.

32
00:02:26,151 --> 00:02:27,591
What is it you want to see me about?

33
00:02:29,950 --> 00:02:30,630
Master,

34
00:02:32,391 --> 00:02:33,670
I want to enter the Xinhuo Palace.

35
00:02:34,630 --> 00:02:36,271
Although I have become Transcendent,

36
00:02:36,470 --> 00:02:37,431
I can't even reach

37
00:02:37,431 --> 00:02:38,311
the ability to

38
00:02:38,350 --> 00:02:39,190
challenge the Hundred-Battle Chamber.

39
00:02:41,470 --> 00:02:43,551
You will only make it

40
00:02:44,271 --> 00:02:45,790
after becoming a Transcendent Knight

41
00:02:45,910 --> 00:02:47,111
and practicing for a while

42
00:02:47,991 --> 00:02:49,551
in a Transcendent organization.

43
00:02:50,831 --> 00:02:52,230
You just became Transcendent

44
00:02:52,950 --> 00:02:54,670
and want to challenge
the Hundred-Battle Chamber?

45
00:02:55,190 --> 00:02:55,871
Master,

46
00:02:56,991 --> 00:02:58,271
I want to enter the Xinhuo Palace

47
00:03:01,230 --> 00:03:02,470
not only to improve my abilities

48
00:03:02,551 --> 00:03:03,470
but also to rescue my mother.

49
00:03:03,910 --> 00:03:04,871
True.

50
00:03:05,711 --> 00:03:06,630
I suspect
that there are Demon Clan spies

51
00:03:06,630 --> 00:03:07,551
in the Xinhuo Palace

52
00:03:07,750 --> 00:03:09,190
and the Elder Council
is in the Xinhuo Palace.

53
00:03:09,871 --> 00:03:10,991
Master, don't worry.

54
00:03:11,391 --> 00:03:11,991
I've never mentioned this

55
00:03:12,070 --> 00:03:13,630
to anyone before.

56
00:03:14,431 --> 00:03:15,510
If there really are Demon Clan spies

57
00:03:15,630 --> 00:03:16,790
in the Xinhuo Palace,

58
00:03:17,311 --> 00:03:18,190
it would be a great threat

59
00:03:18,271 --> 00:03:19,470
to our Xia Clan.

60
00:03:19,991 --> 00:03:21,630
Rescuing my mother is my responsibility,

61
00:03:22,711 --> 00:03:24,230
but finding out the Demon Clan spies

62
00:03:24,431 --> 00:03:26,031
is my mission against the Demon Clan.

63
00:03:27,031 --> 00:03:28,190
(When I was young,)

64
00:03:28,271 --> 00:03:30,790
(I was as determined and brave as him,)

65
00:03:31,111 --> 00:03:32,311
(fearless of everything.)

66
00:03:32,311 --> 00:03:32,950
Now that Great Demon God

67
00:03:33,031 --> 00:03:34,190
wants to make a comeback,

68
00:03:34,910 --> 00:03:35,910
I can no longer

69
00:03:35,910 --> 00:03:36,831
practice alone.

70
00:03:37,470 --> 00:03:38,750
Even if I train to become more powerful,

71
00:03:38,831 --> 00:03:39,910
what's the point?

72
00:03:43,470 --> 00:03:44,831
To enter the Xinhuo Palace,

73
00:03:45,391 --> 00:03:46,190
besides relying on martial arts

74
00:03:46,311 --> 00:03:47,711
and challenging
the Hundred-Battle Chamber,

75
00:03:48,630 --> 00:03:50,391
there are other ways.

76
00:03:51,950 --> 00:03:53,230
To fight against the Demon Clan,

77
00:03:53,391 --> 00:03:55,070
we need not only strength

78
00:03:55,470 --> 00:03:56,591
but also wisdom

79
00:03:56,711 --> 00:03:57,750
and unity.

80
00:03:59,790 --> 00:04:01,151
In the Battle at Xueying Territory,

81
00:04:01,271 --> 00:04:02,750
the Demon Clan opened the Demon Well

82
00:04:02,991 --> 00:04:04,311
and let in demons,

83
00:04:04,551 --> 00:04:05,230
which gave us

84
00:04:05,230 --> 00:04:06,391
a painful lesson.

85
00:04:07,271 --> 00:04:08,271
Now, the Demon Clan's actions

86
00:04:08,271 --> 00:04:09,431
won't stop.

87
00:04:09,630 --> 00:04:10,470
In the future,

88
00:04:10,591 --> 00:04:11,871
the situation will only be worse.

89
00:04:13,311 --> 00:04:14,230
Back then,

90
00:04:15,151 --> 00:04:16,990
the six Elders
who participated in the sealing

91
00:04:17,310 --> 00:04:19,550
connected their lives
to the bronze coffin

92
00:04:20,031 --> 00:04:21,550
and lit the six soul lamps.

93
00:04:22,831 --> 00:04:24,031
The key to unsealing

94
00:04:24,870 --> 00:04:26,631
lies with the six Elders.

95
00:04:27,831 --> 00:04:29,550
The Demon Clan
will definitely do everything

96
00:04:29,670 --> 00:04:30,951
to extinguish those six soul lamps.

97
00:04:31,670 --> 00:04:33,031
What we need to do

98
00:04:33,430 --> 00:04:35,391
is to assemble the six Elders

99
00:04:35,751 --> 00:04:37,031
and work together.

100
00:04:37,550 --> 00:04:39,191
The six elders working together.

101
00:04:40,990 --> 00:04:42,511
Besides Ms. Xiaoxi,

102
00:04:43,790 --> 00:04:45,110
there's also Senior Ye.

103
00:04:45,191 --> 00:04:46,430
Ever since the battle,

104
00:04:47,151 --> 00:04:48,631
Ye Mei has been solitary

105
00:04:48,870 --> 00:04:50,110
and developed her own faction.

106
00:04:50,230 --> 00:04:51,670
She doesn't want to have any connection

107
00:04:51,790 --> 00:04:52,910
with the Elder Council,

108
00:04:53,391 --> 00:04:54,751
let alone working together.

109
00:04:56,071 --> 00:04:56,951
What if

110
00:04:57,470 --> 00:04:58,430
we can invite Senior Ye

111
00:04:58,550 --> 00:04:59,910
back to the Elder Council?

112
00:05:01,711 --> 00:05:02,470
Xueying,

113
00:05:03,430 --> 00:05:04,951
you have already surpassed me,

114
00:05:05,470 --> 00:05:06,191
becoming the youngest Transcendent

115
00:05:06,191 --> 00:05:07,711
of the Xia Clan.

116
00:05:08,191 --> 00:05:09,910
Not to mention your martial arts skills,

117
00:05:10,230 --> 00:05:12,191
in the future,
there's more room for improvement.

118
00:05:12,790 --> 00:05:13,631
However,

119
00:05:14,151 --> 00:05:15,230
relying on bravery,

120
00:05:15,350 --> 00:05:16,910
you can only
make you strong for a moment.

121
00:05:18,350 --> 00:05:20,751
To make the Xia Clan prosperous,

122
00:05:21,031 --> 00:05:22,430
we still need the Elder Council.

123
00:05:23,391 --> 00:05:24,271
If you can find a way

124
00:05:24,271 --> 00:05:26,191
to bring Ye Mei
back to the Elder Council,

125
00:05:26,631 --> 00:05:27,990
entering the Xinhuo Palace

126
00:05:28,430 --> 00:05:29,751
isn't impossible.

127
00:05:31,071 --> 00:05:31,951
I understand.

128
00:05:32,631 --> 00:05:33,310
Master,

129
00:05:34,230 --> 00:05:35,711
please take good care of yourself.

130
00:05:39,751 --> 00:05:40,271
I will take my leave.

131
00:05:40,271 --> 00:05:40,990
Xueying,

132
00:05:44,711 --> 00:05:47,071
Ye Mei is a very stubborn person.

133
00:05:47,271 --> 00:05:48,470
Persuading her

134
00:05:48,591 --> 00:05:49,990
won't be an easy task.

135
00:05:50,670 --> 00:05:52,470
You must have a good approach,

136
00:05:52,591 --> 00:05:53,470
only then can you succeed.

137
00:05:54,430 --> 00:05:55,191
I understand.

138
00:05:58,151 --> 00:05:59,071
Respected Elders,

139
00:05:59,511 --> 00:06:01,071
today I bring Xueying here

140
00:06:01,191 --> 00:06:02,391
because he has an idea

141
00:06:03,031 --> 00:06:04,430
and would like to report to you all.

142
00:06:04,751 --> 00:06:05,350
Tell us.

143
00:06:05,951 --> 00:06:07,670
The Demon Clan's power is surging now.

144
00:06:08,470 --> 00:06:10,631
Please join forces
to fight against them.

145
00:06:11,790 --> 00:06:12,591
The bronze coffin

146
00:06:12,591 --> 00:06:13,670
was initially sealed

147
00:06:13,670 --> 00:06:14,511
by you, six Elders.

148
00:06:14,831 --> 00:06:16,271
It can be said that
you are inseparable in life and death.

149
00:06:16,951 --> 00:06:17,790
However, now,

150
00:06:18,071 --> 00:06:19,711
Elder Ye is alone outside.

151
00:06:20,870 --> 00:06:22,350
With the great enemy,

152
00:06:22,511 --> 00:06:23,670
we should bring Elder Ye

153
00:06:23,670 --> 00:06:24,670
back to the Elder Council

154
00:06:24,870 --> 00:06:26,191
and fight against
the Demon Clan together.

155
00:06:26,430 --> 00:06:27,870
With Ye Mei's temper,

156
00:06:28,031 --> 00:06:30,631
I'm afraid no one can persuade her.

157
00:06:30,751 --> 00:06:32,031
I am willing to give it a try.

158
00:06:34,511 --> 00:06:36,751
You think you can persuade Ye Mei.

159
00:06:37,031 --> 00:06:38,550
Maybe as soon as you open your mouth,

160
00:06:38,711 --> 00:06:40,470
your front teeth will be knocked out

161
00:06:40,591 --> 00:06:41,550
by her wind blade.

162
00:06:42,191 --> 00:06:42,910
Xueying,

163
00:06:43,110 --> 00:06:45,230
your intention is enough.

164
00:06:45,430 --> 00:06:46,151
However...

165
00:06:46,271 --> 00:06:47,350
However, I have a condition.

166
00:06:47,910 --> 00:06:49,591
If I successfully convince Elder Ye

167
00:06:49,670 --> 00:06:50,631
to return to the Elder Council,

168
00:06:51,191 --> 00:06:52,711
then I want to enter the Xinhuo Palace.

169
00:06:57,391 --> 00:06:59,271
What's the point
of entering Xinhuo Palace?

170
00:06:59,391 --> 00:07:00,870
Why not come to
the Black White Deity Mountain?

171
00:07:01,470 --> 00:07:03,271
What are your conditions?
Feel free to tell me.

172
00:07:03,550 --> 00:07:04,631
Please grant my request,

173
00:07:04,790 --> 00:07:05,670
dear Elders.

174
00:07:06,230 --> 00:07:07,470
(This child.)

175
00:07:07,831 --> 00:07:09,350
(His persistence)

176
00:07:09,511 --> 00:07:11,550
(is quite like his mother back then.)

177
00:07:12,511 --> 00:07:14,670
So you want to enter the Xinhuo Palace.

178
00:07:14,990 --> 00:07:15,990
However,

179
00:07:16,071 --> 00:07:16,910
entering Xinhuo Palace

180
00:07:16,990 --> 00:07:18,470
has its own rules.

181
00:07:18,711 --> 00:07:19,870
We can't change them

182
00:07:19,990 --> 00:07:20,951
just for you

183
00:07:21,350 --> 00:07:22,511
casually.

184
00:07:22,790 --> 00:07:24,910
During the war,
we suffered heavy casualties.

185
00:07:25,310 --> 00:07:26,310
Now,

186
00:07:26,550 --> 00:07:27,550
it is the time to

187
00:07:27,631 --> 00:07:29,151
cultivate disciples.

188
00:07:29,751 --> 00:07:30,550
If Xueying

189
00:07:30,550 --> 00:07:31,870
can bring Ye Mei back,

190
00:07:32,031 --> 00:07:33,151
make an exception for him.

191
00:07:33,350 --> 00:07:34,711
Letting him enter Xinhuo Palace

192
00:07:34,831 --> 00:07:36,151
is also understandable.

193
00:07:36,310 --> 00:07:37,910
Chunyuan is right.

194
00:07:38,430 --> 00:07:40,230
No breaking, no establishing.

195
00:07:40,870 --> 00:07:42,350
The most important thing for us now

196
00:07:42,511 --> 00:07:44,550
is to gather forces
to resist the Demon Clan.

197
00:07:45,110 --> 00:07:45,910
Forget about those rules

198
00:07:46,071 --> 00:07:47,230
set in the past.

199
00:07:48,031 --> 00:07:49,831
Any outstanding disciples

200
00:07:50,350 --> 00:07:51,350
should be absorbed

201
00:07:51,470 --> 00:07:53,031
into Xinhuo Palace.

202
00:07:59,191 --> 00:08:00,191
I have no objections.

203
00:08:00,350 --> 00:08:02,470
As Xueying has
such confidence and determination,

204
00:08:02,951 --> 00:08:03,951
respected Elders,

205
00:08:04,110 --> 00:08:05,151
why not give him a chance

206
00:08:05,151 --> 00:08:06,031
to give it a try?

207
00:08:06,550 --> 00:08:07,230
Alright.

208
00:08:07,951 --> 00:08:09,550
If he really succeeds,

209
00:08:09,670 --> 00:08:11,110
it would be a great contribution

210
00:08:11,230 --> 00:08:12,470
to the unity of the Elders.

211
00:08:13,031 --> 00:08:15,110
As long as Ye Mei
agrees to join the Elder Council,

212
00:08:15,751 --> 00:08:18,271
I agree to let you into Xinhuo Palace.

213
00:08:19,951 --> 00:08:21,031
Thank you, Master He.

214
00:08:21,191 --> 00:08:22,230
It depends on whether you have

215
00:08:22,310 --> 00:08:23,310
the ability or not.

216
00:08:29,110 --> 00:08:30,751
I didn't expect the Bloodshed Tavern

217
00:08:30,870 --> 00:08:32,631
to be in such a remote place.

218
00:08:32,871 --> 00:08:33,751
I've been here once before

219
00:08:33,871 --> 00:08:35,231
with Xueying and the Elders.

220
00:08:35,430 --> 00:08:36,670
I didn't feel it then.

221
00:08:36,830 --> 00:08:38,670
But now, walking by myself,

222
00:08:38,790 --> 00:08:40,231
I feel lost,

223
00:08:40,351 --> 00:08:41,631
almost getting confused.

224
00:08:41,910 --> 00:08:42,871
It must have been because

225
00:08:42,871 --> 00:08:43,790
the Elders
who are familiar with the route

226
00:08:43,790 --> 00:08:44,950
were leading the way.

227
00:08:47,430 --> 00:08:48,950
(Why are they here?)

228
00:08:50,830 --> 00:08:52,391
Which way should we go?

229
00:08:53,471 --> 00:08:54,471
Behind that fog,

230
00:08:54,471 --> 00:08:55,430
there seems to be a cabin.

231
00:08:55,430 --> 00:08:56,271
Let's go and have a look.

232
00:08:57,590 --> 00:08:58,111
Let's go.

233
00:09:01,031 --> 00:09:02,511
What are you doing here?

234
00:09:02,631 --> 00:09:03,950
We are going to the Bloodshed Tavern

235
00:09:04,070 --> 00:09:05,031
to find the master, Ye Mei.

236
00:09:05,310 --> 00:09:06,670
What do you want from her?

237
00:09:06,830 --> 00:09:08,511
We have a matter to discuss
with the master.

238
00:09:08,910 --> 00:09:10,351
What is it that you want?

239
00:09:11,271 --> 00:09:12,910
The rules of the Bloodshed Tavern

240
00:09:13,031 --> 00:09:14,910
require leaving a mission and reward.

241
00:09:15,111 --> 00:09:16,871
We've never seen anyone like you

242
00:09:16,991 --> 00:09:18,631
who comes and asks to see
the master right away.

243
00:09:19,231 --> 00:09:21,111
Would you please tell us

244
00:09:21,231 --> 00:09:22,710
the exact location
of the Bloodshed Tavern?

245
00:09:22,991 --> 00:09:23,950
We would be very grateful.

246
00:09:26,871 --> 00:09:28,550
You can go that way.

247
00:09:29,430 --> 00:09:30,151
Thank you.

248
00:09:39,950 --> 00:09:40,430
Let's go.

249
00:09:41,991 --> 00:09:43,351
This is the Bloodshed Tavern?

250
00:09:43,991 --> 00:09:44,871
Don't speak nonsense.

251
00:09:53,310 --> 00:09:54,670
Who are these people?

252
00:09:56,231 --> 00:09:57,670
Why aren't you serving us?

253
00:09:57,790 --> 00:09:59,231
Our Bloodshed Tavern

254
00:09:59,471 --> 00:10:01,070
does not serve outsiders.

255
00:10:01,550 --> 00:10:02,351
We came here today

256
00:10:02,351 --> 00:10:03,430
to find your master.

257
00:10:03,550 --> 00:10:04,430
Please show us the way.

258
00:10:04,590 --> 00:10:06,151
Leave your reward and name.

259
00:10:06,271 --> 00:10:08,070
Our master doesn't see guests.

260
00:10:08,151 --> 00:10:09,151
Who would pay

261
00:10:09,271 --> 00:10:10,231
without seeing the seller first?

262
00:10:10,351 --> 00:10:11,070
Please show us the way

263
00:10:11,190 --> 00:10:12,430
to meet Master Ye.

264
00:10:36,231 --> 00:10:37,910
Since you were able to find this place,

265
00:10:38,031 --> 00:10:39,031
you must have received

266
00:10:39,031 --> 00:10:40,031
Master's approval.

267
00:10:40,590 --> 00:10:42,231
As for how it was granted,

268
00:10:42,391 --> 00:10:43,710
I don't know.

269
00:10:43,910 --> 00:10:44,710
You're saying

270
00:10:44,710 --> 00:10:46,031
like you didn't say anything at all.

271
00:10:54,910 --> 00:10:56,351
You can go that way.

272
00:10:57,391 --> 00:10:58,590
(Could it be her?)

273
00:11:37,430 --> 00:11:39,631
Is playing this tune really helpful?

274
00:11:40,310 --> 00:11:41,471
Let's wait and see.

275
00:11:55,670 --> 00:11:57,830
That's right, she is Senior Ye Mei.

276
00:11:57,950 --> 00:11:58,790
Xueying,

277
00:11:58,910 --> 00:12:00,070
how did you know this tune

278
00:12:00,190 --> 00:12:01,430
would attract Ye Mei?

279
00:12:01,550 --> 00:12:02,950
Master Sikong told me

280
00:12:03,111 --> 00:12:04,550
this is her favorite tune.

281
00:12:04,871 --> 00:12:05,830
Faction Leader?

282
