they sent you here to persuade me.

302
00:12:57,471 --> 00:12:59,310
You are really bold.

303
00:12:59,471 --> 00:13:00,190
While I'm willing to

304
00:13:00,190 --> 00:13:01,631
let you off today,

305
00:13:01,830 --> 00:13:02,991
you had better leave.

306
00:13:03,151 --> 00:13:04,111
The Demon Clan is now invading,

307
00:13:04,231 --> 00:13:05,231
