315
00:13:21,871 --> 00:13:22,871
(with Bloodshed God Emperor.)

316
00:13:22,950 --> 00:13:24,351
(They were in perfect harmony.)

317
00:13:24,538 --> 00:13:26,578
(A perfect match.)

318
00:13:27,578 --> 00:13:29,178
(However, when the Demon Clan invaded,)

319
00:13:29,298 --> 00:13:31,218
(everyone chose Hero Shan)

320
00:13:31,458 --> 00:13:32,779
(who had both martial arts and wisdom)

321
00:13:32,938 --> 00:13:35,298
(to infiltrate the Demon Clan
for information.)

322
00:13:45,114 --> 00:13:46,154
(In the end, Xinhuo Palace)

323
00:13:46,274 --> 00:13:48,274
(successfully destroyed
the Demon Clan's nest,)

324
00:13:48,595 --> 00:13:51,754
(but Hero Shan died
from his severe injuries.)

325
00:13:51,874 --> 00:13:52,874
Shan!

326
00:13:53,715 --> 00:13:54,595
Shan.

327
00:13:55,634 --> 00:13:56,715
Shan.

328
00:14:03,915 --> 00:14:06,315
