330
00:14:08,114 --> 00:14:09,274
(the Bloodshed Tavern.)

331
00:14:09,435 --> 00:14:10,754
(She led a solitary life,)

332
00:14:10,955 --> 00:14:12,394
(cutting off ties with the world.)

333
00:14:12,675 --> 00:14:13,514
Senior Ye,

334
00:14:13,955 --> 00:14:14,754
now the Demon Clan

335
00:14:14,874 --> 00:14:16,354
has broken through the Demon Well

336
00:14:16,675 --> 00:14:17,715
and the bronze coffin

337
00:14:17,874 --> 00:14:19,234
has been transported to
the Dragon Mountain Empire.

338
00:14:19,835 --> 00:14:21,234
At this critical moment,

339
00:14:21,394 --> 00:14:22,435
we are here

340
00:14:22,555 --> 00:14:23,835
to invite you, Senior Ye,

341
00:14:23,955 --> 00:14:24,835
to come back,

342
00:14:24,915 --> 00:14:25,874
uniting with other sects

343
00:14:25,994 --> 00:14:27,154
and fighting against
the Demon Clan together.

344
00:14:28,394 --> 00:14:29,994
I have nothing to do with them anymore.

345
00:14:30,274 --> 00:14:31,435
The Xinhuo Palace

346
00:14:31,595 --> 00:14:32,835
has nothing to do with me either.

347
00:14:32,955 --> 00:14:34,595
But you are a member of the Xia Clan.

348
00:14:35,195 --> 00:14:36,634
This is related to
the Xia Clan's territory

349
00:14:36,795 --> 00:14:38,034
and the people of

350
00:14:38,195 --> 00:14:39,034
the Dragon Mountain Empire.

351
00:14:39,274 --> 00:14:40,675
Doesn't this concern you?

352
00:14:41,715 --> 00:14:43,955
Senior Ye, please reconsider.

353
00:14:45,634 --> 00:14:46,595
No need.

354
00:14:47,675 --> 00:14:48,435
Senior.

