361
00:15:44,555 --> 00:15:46,034
This place holds
the most beautiful memories

362
00:15:46,034 --> 00:15:47,032
of her and Hero Shan.

363
00:15:47,226 --> 00:15:48,305
So, Hero Shan

364
00:15:48,545 --> 00:15:50,466
