making Senior Ye worried and sad.

365
00:15:50,666 --> 00:15:51,865
That's why he made up his mind.

366
00:15:52,345 --> 00:15:54,105
A man like Hero Shan

367
00:15:54,305 --> 00:15:55,785
is indeed a rare nice man.

368
00:16:01,266 --> 00:16:02,105
(Mei,)

369
00:16:02,986 --> 00:16:04,666
(this is the formation I left for you.)

370
00:16:05,186 --> 00:16:06,666
(I hope you can use it)

371
00:16:06,906 --> 00:16:08,345
