374
00:16:12,865 --> 00:16:13,585
(These bamboo leaves)

375
00:16:13,585 --> 00:16:14,906
(can help you escape safely.)

376
00:16:16,226 --> 00:16:17,305
(I have hidden)

377
00:16:17,305 --> 00:16:18,305
(these sealed memory bubbles)

378
00:16:18,545 --> 00:16:19,825
(inside the bamboo leaves.)

379
00:16:20,426 --> 00:16:21,865
(I really hope you won't see them.)

380
00:16:22,825 --> 00:16:23,825
(Even if I can't)

381
00:16:23,825 --> 00:16:24,946
(stay by your side forever,)

382
00:16:25,385 --> 00:16:26,545
(these memories)

383
00:16:27,026 --> 00:16:28,145
(won't disappear.)

384
00:16:28,545 --> 00:16:29,666
So that's it.

385
00:16:31,385 --> 00:16:32,426
Shan,

386
00:16:33,065 --> 00:16:34,186
I knew it.

387
00:16:35,065 --> 00:16:36,186
You wouldn't be so cruel

388
00:16:36,186 --> 00:16:37,186
and left me behind.

389
00:16:38,065 --> 00:16:39,865
Hero Shan did it to protect you

