391
00:16:41,226 --> 00:16:42,385
our fellow Xia Clan members.

392
00:16:42,666 --> 00:16:43,666
Senior Ye Mei,

393
00:16:44,026 --> 00:16:45,426
I, Dongbo Xueying,

394
00:16:45,666 --> 00:16:46,625
implore you

395
00:16:47,145 --> 00:16:48,785
to return to the Elder Council with us.

396
00:16:50,105 --> 00:16:52,026
