402
00:16:58,506 --> 00:16:59,226
Now,

403
00:16:59,385 --> 00:17:00,266
the other Elders

404
00:17:00,266 --> 00:17:01,466
also need your help.

405
00:17:02,946 --> 00:17:04,625
To live and die together

406
00:17:06,625 --> 00:17:08,666
is just a sugar-coated promise.

407
00:17:11,746 --> 00:17:12,625
However,

408
00:17:13,226 --> 00:17:14,865
I can agree

409
00:17:15,585 --> 00:17:16,865
to go back

410
00:17:17,105 --> 00:17:19,065
and take a look

411
00:17:19,785 --> 00:17:21,466
at how the Elder Council is now.

412
00:17:27,545 --> 00:17:29,226
We've been monitoring for so long,

413
00:17:29,666 --> 00:17:31,666
yet the Demon Clan
still found a loophole.

414
00:17:31,865 --> 00:17:33,305
Ao Lan took the bronze coffin

415
00:17:33,305 --> 00:17:34,585
and left Xueying Territory.

416
00:17:34,706 --> 00:17:36,585
With enemies lurking in the dark,

417
00:17:37,186 --> 00:17:39,065
we must find a solution.

418
00:17:39,226 --> 00:17:40,345
The bronze coffin

419
00:17:40,506 --> 00:17:41,785
is extremely important to
the Demon Clan.

420
00:17:41,986 --> 00:17:42,825
I think

421
00:17:43,065 --> 00:17:44,305
Ao Lan must have taken the coffin

422
00:17:44,426 --> 00:17:45,545
back to the Demon God Association,

423
00:17:45,906 --> 00:17:47,986
but the Demon God Association
is hidden in the darkness.

424
00:17:48,145 --> 00:17:48,906
We might need

425
00:17:48,906 --> 00:17:50,305
a lot of effort to find it.

426
00:17:50,545 --> 00:17:52,186
Unexpectedly,
the Black White Deity Mountain

427
00:17:52,305 --> 00:17:54,065
has produced such scum as Moyang Chen.

428
00:17:54,385 --> 00:17:55,666
Otherwise, we wouldn't have

429
00:17:55,865 --> 00:17:57,426
watched the bronze coffin

430
00:17:57,585 --> 00:17:59,105
get lost right under our noses.

431
00:17:59,266 --> 00:18:00,065
What a waste

432
00:18:00,065 --> 00:18:01,385
of Tai Shu's sacrifice.

433
00:18:01,545 --> 00:18:02,746
The Black White Deity Mountain

434
00:18:02,865 --> 00:18:04,065
to cultivate such a disgraceful disciple

435
00:18:04,585 --> 00:18:05,946
is my negligence.

436
00:18:06,706 --> 00:18:07,666
I will find the Demon God Association

437
00:18:07,666 --> 00:18:08,785
and Moyang Chen

438
00:18:08,986 --> 00:18:10,266
as soon as possible

439
00:18:10,906 --> 00:18:12,426
to clean up the mess

440
00:18:12,545 --> 00:18:13,785
for our Black White Deity Mountain.

441
00:18:14,466 --> 00:18:15,345
Master He,

442
00:18:15,506 --> 00:18:16,986
there's no need to
blame yourself too much.

443
00:18:17,385 --> 00:18:17,986
As for the Demon God Association,

444
00:18:17,986 --> 00:18:19,305
if it were that easy to find,

445
00:18:19,466 --> 00:18:20,785
the Demon Clan
would have been uprooted long ago.

446
00:18:20,785 --> 00:18:21,266
Could it be

447
00:18:21,266 --> 00:18:22,986
that after more than twenty years,

448
00:18:23,186 --> 00:18:24,186
you still haven't found out

449
00:18:24,186 --> 00:18:25,426
where the Demon God Association is?

450
00:18:30,105 --> 00:18:32,105
Ye Mei, you're here.

451
00:18:32,305 --> 00:18:34,506
Why? Don't welcome me?

452
00:18:34,785 --> 00:18:36,585
If it weren't for that Dongbo Xueying

453
00:18:36,585 --> 00:18:37,746
who convinced me to come,

454
00:18:37,825 --> 00:18:39,186
I wouldn't have been willing to come.

455
00:18:40,026 --> 00:18:41,226
I really didn't expect

456
00:18:41,585 --> 00:18:43,305
that Xueying actually convinced you

457
00:18:43,426 --> 00:18:45,266
to return to
the Xinhuo Palace Elder Council.

458
00:18:45,506 --> 00:18:48,065
The great war between Xia and the demons
is about to break out.

459
00:18:48,345 --> 00:18:50,305
I'm afraid that Elder Sikong

460
00:18:50,466 --> 00:18:51,825
needs another sacrificial pawn,

461
00:18:51,825 --> 00:18:52,946
don't you?

462
00:18:53,226 --> 00:18:53,706
You...

463
00:18:53,746 --> 00:18:55,426
It's a good thing
for Ye Mei to come back.

464
00:18:56,466 --> 00:18:58,385
Now the five clans' power is damaged.

465
00:18:58,625 --> 00:18:59,666
One more force,

466
00:19:00,305 --> 00:19:02,385
the more chances we have
to fight against the Demon Clan.

467
00:19:02,666 --> 00:19:03,545
At this time,

468
00:19:03,785 --> 00:19:05,305
we should be more united.

469
00:19:06,065 --> 00:19:07,226
For the location of
the Demon God Association

470
00:19:07,226 --> 00:19:09,065
you mentioned,

471
00:19:09,305 --> 00:19:10,065
maybe

472
00:19:10,065 --> 00:19:11,865
I can provide some clues.

