in common after death.

479
00:19:22,226 --> 00:19:23,785
No heart blood.

480
00:19:23,946 --> 00:19:25,226
Heart blood?

481
00:19:25,385 --> 00:19:26,506
And he has a particular preference

482
00:19:26,666 --> 00:19:28,986
