Mr. Qin, rest assured.

484
00:19:30,706 --> 00:19:30,865
(Yinglan Pavilion)

485
00:19:30,865 --> 00:19:31,865
(Yinglan Pavilion)
The mission you asked for

486
00:19:32,026 --> 00:19:33,105
will definitely be completed

487
00:19:33,186 --> 00:19:34,065
on the fifteenth of this month.

488
00:19:34,506 --> 00:19:37,105
I can rest assured
with Master Ye handling things.

489
00:19:47,426 --> 00:19:50,105
After eavesdropping for so long,

490
00:19:50,266 --> 00:19:51,186
