491
00:19:51,305 --> 00:19:52,506
I'll take this order.

492
00:19:52,666 --> 00:19:54,226
It's just a small order.

493
00:19:54,345 --> 00:19:56,385
It's not your turn, Hero Xiang.

494
00:19:56,706 --> 00:19:57,946
Let someone else do it.

495
00:19:58,105 --> 00:19:59,026
I want to take it.

496
00:19:59,545 --> 00:20:00,785
I don't care about the price.

497
00:20:01,625 --> 00:20:03,026
As long as the timing is right.

498
00:20:03,746 --> 00:20:06,105
Actually, I've always been curious

499
00:20:06,266 --> 00:20:07,506
