for killing your father?

505
00:20:17,785 --> 00:20:18,706
No need to ask more questions.

506
00:20:18,906 --> 00:20:20,065
Anyway, I want to take the order.

507
00:20:20,785 --> 00:20:22,426
I'll set the price then.

508
00:20:22,625 --> 00:20:23,625
Deal.

509
00:20:24,345 --> 00:20:25,266
At that time,

510
00:20:25,266 --> 00:20:25,946
I just felt

511
00:20:26,026 --> 00:20:27,545
he had some unspeakable secret.

512
00:20:27,585 --> 00:20:28,986
Now that I think about it,

513
00:20:29,585 --> 00:20:31,105
I'm afraid it's not that simple.

514
00:20:31,305 --> 00:20:32,825
Killing on full moon nights

515
00:20:32,986 --> 00:20:34,545
and taking the heart blood away.

516
00:20:34,746 --> 00:20:36,145
According to ancient records,

517
00:20:36,385 --> 00:20:37,545
on the night of the full moon,

518
00:20:37,706 --> 00:20:39,266
