522
00:20:46,345 --> 00:20:47,466
Could this be one of the methods

523
00:20:47,466 --> 00:20:48,466
the Demon Clan uses

524
00:20:48,466 --> 00:20:49,466
to hide their demonic smell?

525
00:20:49,625 --> 00:20:50,666
I think so too.

526
00:20:50,946 --> 00:20:51,906
So, we can

527
00:20:51,906 --> 00:20:52,865
take advantage of this

528
00:20:52,865 --> 00:20:53,986
