531
00:20:57,226 --> 00:20:58,305
Then...

532
00:20:58,426 --> 00:20:59,545
Pretend to retreat,

533
00:20:59,585 --> 00:21:00,466
follow the demon,

534
00:21:00,785 --> 00:21:03,065
and we can find the location
of the Demon God Association.

535
00:21:03,426 --> 00:21:04,865
I've already given you the clue

536
00:21:04,865 --> 00:21:06,026
and I am back too.

537
00:21:06,186 --> 00:21:07,026
You all

538
00:21:07,186 --> 00:21:08,946
