539
00:21:09,266 --> 00:21:10,305
What promise?

540
00:21:10,466 --> 00:21:13,746
Let Dongbo Xueying enter Xinhuo Palace.

541
00:21:15,585 --> 00:21:16,065
Xueying's performance

542
00:21:16,065 --> 00:21:17,825
during
Transcendent Battle of Life and Death

543
00:21:17,986 --> 00:21:19,305
is clear to everyone.

544
00:21:19,545 --> 00:21:20,305
If

545
00:21:20,466 --> 00:21:21,825
he could really enter Xinhuo Palace

546
00:21:21,825 --> 00:21:22,825
to recuperate properly,

547
00:21:23,105 --> 00:21:23,865
maybe

548
00:21:23,865 --> 00:21:24,666
he could become

549
00:21:24,666 --> 00:21:25,746
a powerful helper

550
00:21:25,785 --> 00:21:26,746
for our righteous sects

551
00:21:26,746 --> 00:21:27,666
as Knight Changfeng.

552
00:21:27,986 --> 00:21:29,506
True, but

553
00:21:30,026 --> 00:21:31,145
that Chi Qiubai could make it

554
00:21:31,145 --> 00:21:33,466
doesn't mean Dongbo Xueying can either.

555
00:21:33,666 --> 00:21:34,825
Don't forget

556
00:21:35,226 --> 00:21:37,426
Dongbo Xueying is still young.

557
00:21:37,545 --> 00:21:39,746
Youth represents potential

558
00:21:39,946 --> 00:21:41,865
and infinite possibilities.

559
00:21:42,145 --> 00:21:42,946
Ye Mei,

560
00:21:43,065 --> 00:21:44,105
can you tell me

561
00:21:44,226 --> 00:21:46,226
